  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad Behrni/ klaufajt\nman/ vü nemmeet wehrā to\nWaiiodu mannas Muttes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid tawa Sir̈ds us win-\nnas Zelfkeim ne nomalda/ un ne\napallojees us winnas Pehdahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo winna irr dauds ee-\nwainojſi un pagahsuſi/ un wiſſa-\nDee Warrenee irr no winnas\nnomahkti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnas Nams irr Zelfki\nus Elles/ kas nowadda Nahwes\nKambard̈s.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta VIII. Nodalla.\nTa Deewa Gudriba patti sau/ mubs laipnigi\npee ſerwis : 1. Un apleezina/ ka winna jo\nlabbaka effune fa Pehrles : 7/ 11. Poſar,\nguß arridsan no wiſſeem Grehkeem : 13.\nUn dohdus labbu Padohmu eekſch wiſſahm\nBuhſchanahm : 14/ 15. Mahza Rehninus\nun Leel-Kungus/ fa teem buhs waldiht : 15.\nWiſe ar weenu Wahrbu jafkoht/ ta irr no\nMubſchibas pee Decwa bijusi/ un ihpaschi\neekſch Raddiſchanas Leetahm fawu Spehku\nparahdiuſi : 22.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eggi ta Gudriba sau-\nka/ un ta Sapraſchana\nApazekt fawu Balſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Augsto Weeto Wir̈s Gal-\nlā Zettmalli us Zetta-Juhtim\nstahw winna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sahnis Wahrtim preekſch\nPilsfahta/ kur zaar Durvim\nja-ee-eet brehz winna ſkanri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Us jums juhs Wiht fan-\nfaju es/ un manna Balſs eet us\nteem Zilweſtu Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nemmeet wehrā juhs Ne-\nnojehgas to Gudribu/ un juhs\nZeffi ſaprohteet to ar Sir̈di.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klaufastees/ jo es grivb\naugſtas Leetas isrunnahrt/ un a\ndarriht fawas Luhpas no pare\njahm Leetahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo manna Mutte ru-\nnahs apdohtmigi to Bateefibu\nun ta Besdeehiba irr mannah\nLuhpahm weena Negantiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſa Walloha manna\nMuttes stahiw eekſch Taifniba-\neekſch tahs ne irr nekas pahrweb-\ntihts ned̈s pahrgrohſihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta irr wiſſa taifna tam\nkas to ſaproht/ un pareſa teen\nkas Atſihſchanu attohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peekemmeet mannu P\nmahzischannu labbaki ne ka Su-\nrabu/ un Atſihſchanu wair\nne ka iſlaſfitu Seltn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Gudriba irr labba-\nne ka Pehrles/ un wiſſ/ ko\nwarretohs eegrıbbetees ne irr\nto lihdsinajama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es Gudriba peemahjo\npee Samannaſ/ un es atrohn\napdohtmiga Prahta Sinn-\ntchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta KUNGA Biſjaſch\nna irr/ eenihdeht to Launu/ Le-\nntbu un Gresnibu/ un to fau\nZelfu/ es arri eenihſtu pahrwe-\ntitu Mutti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Padohms un pastah-\nga Buhſhana peederr man/\nesmu ta Sapraſchana/ m\npeederr tas Stiprums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zaur mann walda\nRehnini/ un tee Walditaji eez\nTaifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zaur mann walda\n"
    }
  ],
